---
// Social Proof & Testimonials Section
---

<section class="testimonials-section">
  <div class="testimonials-header">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Trusted by Property Owners</p>
    <h2>Real Results from Real Landlords</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">See how quarterly inspections help property owners catch issues early and save thousands</p>
  </div>

  <div class="testimonials-grid">
    <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
    <div class="testimonial-card">
      <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
      <p class="testimonial-text">
        The quarterly inspection caught a small roof leak before it became a major problem. Saved me at least $8,000 in potential water damage repairs. The 24-hour turnaround is incredible.
      </p>
      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <div class="author-avatar">SJ</div>
        <div class="author-info">
          <div class="author-name">Sarah Johnson</div>
          <div class="author-title">3 Properties in Seattle</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-badge">Saved $8,000+</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
    <div class="testimonial-card featured">
      <div class="featured-badge">Most Popular</div>
      <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
      <p class="testimonial-text">
        As a property manager handling 12 units, the dashboard is a game-changer. I can see all properties at once, track issues over time, and show owners detailed photo reports. Worth every penny.
      </p>
      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <div class="author-avatar">MR</div>
        <div class="author-info">
          <div class="author-name">Michael Rodriguez</div>
          <div class="author-title">Property Manager, 12 Units</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-badge">12 Properties Managed</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
    <div class="testimonial-card">
      <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
      <p class="testimonial-text">
        Found a major HVAC issue during the winter quarterly inspection. The detailed photos and recommendations helped me get it fixed fast. Tenants stayed comfortable and happy.
      </p>
      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <div class="author-avatar">DL</div>
        <div class="author-info">
          <div class="author-name">David Lee</div>
          <div class="author-title">Rental Property Owner</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-badge">Issue Caught Early</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Results Stats Bar -->
  <div class="results-bar">
    <div class="result-stat">
      <div class="result-number">94%</div>
      <div class="result-label">Issues Found Early</div>
    </div>
    <div class="result-stat">
      <div class="result-number">$12K</div>
      <div class="result-label">Avg. Savings/Year</div>
    </div>
    <div class="result-stat">
      <div class="result-number">200+</div>
      <div class="result-label">Properties Inspected</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    padding: 8rem 3rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .testimonials-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  body.light-mode .section-eyebrow {
    color: #666666;
  }

  .testimonials-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #94a3b8 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  body.light-mode .testimonials-header h2 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #333333 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  body.light-mode .section-subtitle {
    color: #4a4a4a;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .testimonial-card.featured {
    border-color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.05) 0%,
      rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.03) 100%);
  }

  .testimonial-card.featured:hover {
    border-color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
  }

  body.light-mode .testimonial-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  body.light-mode .testimonial-card.featured {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border-color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
  }

  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.4);
  }

  .quote-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }

  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  body.light-mode .testimonial-text {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #475569 0%, #334155 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  body.light-mode .author-avatar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
  }

  .author-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .author-name {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .author-title {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  body.light-mode .author-title {
    color: #666666;
  }

  .result-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
    color: rgb(16, 185, 129);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  }

  body.light-mode .result-badge {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
  }

  /* Results Stats Bar */
  .results-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.08) 0%,
      rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.04) 100%);
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.15);
  }

  body.light-mode .results-bar {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .result-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .result-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .result-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  body.light-mode .result-label {
    color: #4a4a4a;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-section {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .testimonial-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .results-bar {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .result-number {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
